OL,3,CI'd have stayed on if I knew we
OL,4,Cwouldn't be independent 10 years on `
OL,5,CSalmond
OL,7,FFormer first minister Alex Salmond has
OL,8,Fsaid he would have stayed on in the
OL,9,Frole after the 2014 referendum if he
OL,10,Fknew Scotland would still not be
OL,11,Findependent after a decade.
OL,13,FMr Salmond made the decision to step
OL,14,Fdown the day after the vote ` which
OL,15,Fthe Yes campaign lost by 55% to 45%.
OL,17,FBut in recent months, he has described
OL,18,Fthe move as a "mistake".
