OL,5,CSalmond
OL,7,FSpeaking in a new documentary by ITV
OL,8,FBorder about the 10th anniversary of
OL,9,Fthe independence referendum ` named A
OL,10,FDecade of Debate ` Mr Salmond said he
OL,11,Fwould not have handed off the reins to
OL,12,Fdeputy Nicola Sturgeon at the time had
OL,13,Fhe known how the next 10 years would
OL,14,Fplay out.
OL,16,F"I thought to make a point of
OL,17,Fdeparture for the referendum in the
OL,18,Ffuture was a right thing for the
OL,19,Fnational movement. Looking back, that
OL,20,Fwas a mistake," he said.
