OL,3,CI'd have stayed on if I knew we
OL,4,Cwouldn't be independent 10 years on `
OL,5,CSalmond
OL,7,F"Now, in retrospect, that was a daft
OL,8,Fthing to do. But then... I thought we
OL,9,Fwere set for independence in a
OL,10,Freasonable timescale."
OL,12,FHe added: "If you'd told me then that
OL,13,Ften years later, we'd still be waiting
OL,14,Fdespite the manifest opportunities
OL,15,Fthere have been, then I would have
OL,16,Fsaid, 'well, I'll just hang about then
OL,17,Fand see the matter through."
OL,19,FBut Ms Sturgeon questioned if that
OL,20,Fwould be the case.
