OL,5,CSalmond
OL,7,F"So clearly he's going to think that
OL,8,Fhe could have done things so much
OL,9,Fbetter. I say that in as gentle a way
OL,10,Fas possible, to coin one of his
OL,11,Ffavourite phrases," she told the
OL,12,Fdocumentary.
OL,14,FMs Sturgeon also spoke of how she was
OL,15,Funsure if she wanted to step into Mr
OL,16,FSalmond's shoes when he decided to
OL,17,Fstand down.
